DefaultEvent.Description: The moves; the consequences; the risks; the relics. Death is difficult on the Unterzee, but now you know more of it than you ever expected.

ChildBranches.Name: Read the Boke
ChildBranches.Description: Some of the stains are so old that they no longer smell. Some of the writing is still legible. [This will increase your Iron to 60.]

DefaultEvent.Description: Mm. Yes. Ouch. Mm. My. Well, he deserved it. Good Lord. Good Lord. Hmm. Really? Well.

ChildBranches.Name: Read the Boke
ChildBranches.Description: You're a soldier. This is your business. [This will increase your Iron to 85.]

Description: Some previous zee-captain acquired this horrendous compendium. Where, you'll never know. That's for the best.
Name: Read the Boke of Sharpes
